schools.name: T W Kelly Dirigo Middle School

data.description: Nestled in a serene setting, this charming residence offers more than just a home; it provides a lifestyle of comfort and leisure. The focal point of the property is undoubtedly the inviting inground pool, creating a private oasis where relaxation and enjoyment become a daily indulgence. The convenience of a garage adds a practical touch, ensuring your vehicles are sheltered from the elements. Moreover, the property boasts extra space, versatile enough to accommodate various endeavors or serve as a dedicated storage area. For added flexibility, you could even consider converting this extra space into an in-law apartment or studio. Nature enthusiasts will delight in the proximity to the Sugarloaf's Hiking Trails, providing an opportunity to explore the great outdoors right from your back yard. Additionally, the property offers direct ATV and snowmobile access, allowing you to seamlessly embark on exciting adventures from your doorstep. Centrally located to Auburn and Portland areas, this residence provides convenient access to urban amenities. Furthermore, within just an hour's drive, you can reach three renowned ski mountains, adding to the allure of this well-rounded living space. With its combination of functional amenities, a serene ambiance, and access to recreational activities, this residence truly embodies a comfortable and convenient lifestyle.
